song_lyrics: Re het karī kahe chhe Rasiyo, vahālo māro rudiyāmā vasiyo re... Het° ṭek
Re Akṣhar ākāsh ṭhekāṇe, re māyā mahā shūnya paramāṇe;
Mukta koṭi vījaḷiyu jāṇe... Re het° 1
Re pakṣhī te anant puruṣh lekho, re aṣhṭāvaraṇ dehane dekho;
Re sthir ne asthir gatiyu rahe chhe, re kāḷ shakti tene kahe chhe;
Buddhivant samajīne lahe chhe... Re het° 3
Re nirguṇ saguṇ samajī letā, re te sarave Akṣharne ke’tā;
Swatantar pote sadā rahetā... Re het° 4
Re kāḷe māyā kṣhobhane pāme, re anant brahmānḍ thāe tāme;
Em kahyu Premsakhīne Shyāme... Re het° 5
title: Re het karī kahe chhe Rasiyo

1-449: Sadguru Premanand Swami
